description.value:
Outlines safe warp routes and travel times. Good Craftmanship gives +10 to Navigation (Stellar/Warp) Tests, Best Craftsmanship gives +20.

Requirements

Considered incredibly valuable, lost maps may hide hidden routes to places unknown.

Effect: Very Rare

Notes: priceless
